Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:01.33,Small-Title,,0,0,0,,{\K178\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs40\pos(640,723)\c&H2E2E2E&}聖母的慈悲將減輕所有的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:11.66,Comment,,0,0,0,,TCTCDBPTT ROGBWIMAATH
